瑞恩·雷诺兹认为这是奥斯卡有史以来最大的冷落https://www.nme.com/news/film/this-is-what-ryan-reynolds- believes-is-the-biggest-oscars-snub-of-all-time-3811164?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=这就是瑞安·雷诺兹认为的有史以来最大的奥斯卡冷落Chris EdwardsFri, 08 Nov 2024 22:02:12 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvel Cinematic Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3811164 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑞安·雷诺兹" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “最大的不公正之一”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/this-is-what-ryan-reynolds-believes-is-the-biggest-oscars-snub-of-all-time-3811164">瑞恩·雷诺兹 (Ryan Reynolds) 认为这是奥斯卡有史以来最大的冷落，</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="瑞安·雷诺兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/ryan_reynolds_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">瑞恩·雷诺兹</a>透露了他认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>有史以来最大的冷落。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877"><b>《死侍与金刚狼》评论：一部讽刺的、跳过时间的超级英雄讽刺剧</b></a></li></ul><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/deadpool-and-wolverine"><em>《死侍》和《金刚狼》的</em></a>明星在<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/awards/ryan-reynolds-oscars-host-deadpool-wolverine-snub-1236203028/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《<em>综艺</em></a>》 <a id="auto-tag_awards-circuit-podcast" href="https://variety.com/t/awards-circuit-podcast/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-tag="awards-circuit-podcast">颁奖典礼播客</a>上发表讲话时表示，他希望看到更多的喜剧得到学院的认可，这让他分享了他最大的冷落。</p><p> “最大、最、最大的不公正之一是艾迪·墨菲没有因《疯狂教授》获得奥斯卡奖，”他说。 </p><p><iframe title="疯狂教授 |艾迪·墨菲饰演整个克伦普家族" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UpsRucjmTw4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>雷诺兹也在播客中透露，他和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">休·杰克曼</a>正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ryan-reynolds-and-hugh-jackman-are-teaming-up-for-another-film-3809894">合作拍摄另一部</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel">漫威</a>无关的电影。</p><p>在被问及是否愿意有一天主持奥斯卡颁奖典礼后，他回答说：“有一天能主持奥斯卡颁奖典礼将是一个梦想。但我正在为自己、休[杰克曼]和肖恩[利维]写一部电影，这不是漫威。就是这样。”</p><p>这位演员现阶段没有透露任何情节细节，但表示他将在明年参与该项目。</p><p>这部电影也将是雷诺兹继<i>《死侍3》</i> 、 <i>《自由人》</i>和<i>《亚当计划》之后与利维合作的第三部作品。</i> </p><figure id="attachment_3772937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3772937" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine.jpg" alt="《死侍与金刚狼》" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/deadpool_and_wolverine-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772937" class="wp-caption-text">瑞恩·雷诺兹和休·杰克曼在《死侍与金刚狼》中。图片来源：Jay Maidment/20 世纪工作室</figcaption></figure><p><i>《死侍与金刚狼》</i>在电影院取得了巨大成功，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-lively">雷诺兹和布蕾克·莱弗利最近成为继布鲁斯·威利斯和黛米·摩尔之后第一对登上美国票房冠军的夫妇</a>。</p><p> <i>《死侍与金刚狼》</i>位居榜首，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-lively">莱弗利</a>的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/it-ends-with-us"><i>我们的结局》</i></a>获得第二名，这是<i>自 1990 年《虎胆龙威 2》和《人鬼情未了》占据前两名以来首次实现这一壮举。</i></p><p> <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877">在对<i>《死侍与金刚狼》</i>的三星级评论中</a>写道：“尽管有一流的干扰（这里没有剧透）， <i>《死侍与金刚狼》</i>实际上都是关于雷诺兹和杰克曼的。事实上，这一切都是关于雷诺兹的——杰克曼扮演了一个英勇的角色，扮演了一个乖戾的直男，试图跟上雷诺兹扮演的脏话杀手小丑的步伐。前两部<i>《死侍》</i>电影有趣、暴力且原创，但这一部展现了漫威最光荣的不合时宜的超级英雄最好和最坏的一面。</p><p>最近，雷诺兹还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ryan-reynolds-explains-why-he-cut-rob-mcelhenney-cameo-from-deadpool-wolverine-3787243">公开了为什么他必须剪掉<em>《死侍与金刚狼》中罗布·麦克尔亨尼的客串。</em></a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/this-is-what-ryan-reynolds-believes-is-the-biggest-oscars-snub-of-all-time-3811164">瑞恩·雷诺兹 (Ryan Reynolds) 认为这是奥斯卡有史以来最大的冷落，</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
